location.fullValue: Lennox Plan, Siena Reserve : Fontaine Collection

data.description: Beautiful, bright, spacious 2 story single family home in ARTESA, 2 car garage, gated community. Upgraded with window treatments, lighting fixtures, High ceilinged entrance, Quartz counter tops in kitchen, Stainless Steel appliances, porcelain tile on first floor, laminated wood floors upstairs, GAZEBO WITH INSTALLED BRAZILIAN BARBEQUE. Large backyard with space for pool and boat. Gated community with jogging paths, picnic & BBQ area, Excellent location, easy access to major roadways & Turnpike, Black Point marina, the Florida Keys, Homestead Baptist Hospital, restaurants, shopping. Spectacular Club House: gym, basketball, pool, party room, kid's pool. Well lighted streets and Jogging paths within the community.
